{"tid":1675791,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街！譚仔都唔食得啦！","createTime":"2019-10-26T06:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T07:50:30.000Z","uid":203288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"11e240a1fdc4105e2abfed29c8dbaac87d2cdec1","tid":1675791,"uid":203288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nKuXxNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnKuXxNg.jpg&h=1fc83ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n================ <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.marugame.hk/contactus.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.marugame.hk%2Fcontactus.php&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=ff2280c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.marugame.hk/contactus.php</a><br />\n有得留言啊！快尐問爆佢啦<br />\n===================<br />\n丸龜制面公共關係課聯絡人︰<br />\n<br />\n就本人於2019年10月26日於觀塘台，旗下之譚仔雲南米線門外拍攝之一張告示；以致全港所有分店均張貼有關吞示，現作出以下投訴︰<br />\n1) 要求公開解釋不招待曱甴之言論，是指向那一方面特質的客戶；<br />\n2) 要求公開解釋不招待不文明人士之言論，是指向那一方面特質的客戶；<br />\n3) 要求公開解釋客戶自省之言論<br />\n4) 如貴  企業不公開以全港13份報章頭版廣告解釋及道歉，將發動全港市民罷食，直至另行通知<br />\n<br />\n不便之處敬請自省<br />\n<br />\n一名香港市民上<br />\n2019年10月26日<br />\n相片︰<a href=\"http://bit.ly/31Nv223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F31Nv223&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=8ec23813\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/31Nv223</a>"},{"pid":"418e73e8ce2527e2e841d4aca1c10ff7963e89db","tid":1675791,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:15:44.000Z","msg":"不嬲唔食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n貼過就抵你死, 道乜撚歉都冇用, 你估好似立會咁可以彈出彈入收回呀?"},{"pid":"0078c6b765cfb82f0c5048f474575140d5f86fbe","tid":1675791,"uid":264635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"回應左"},{"pid":"3322adb375243ec9539b55a099500209ce18d44c","tid":1675791,"uid":276916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply